@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@productId = p1
@categoryId = fashion

### Categories
# @name listCategories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/catalog/categories

### Products — first page
# @name listProducts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/catalog/products?page=1&page_size=20&sort=name

### Products filtered by category
# @name productsByCategory
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/catalog/products?category_id={{categoryId}}&page=1&page_size=20

### Search products
# @name searchProducts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/catalog/products?q=linen&page=1&page_size=20

### Product detail
# @name getProduct
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/catalog/products/{{productId}}

### Related products
# @name relatedProducts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/catalog/products/{{productId}}/related?limit=4

### Promotions
# @name listPromos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/catalog/promos

### Not found example — expected HTTP 404
# @name missingProduct
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/catalog/products/not-a-real-product
